
Filebeat Setup in KSA:

##### --------------- Filebeat Installation and Configs --------------- #####

ðŸ”¹ 1. Download Filebeat 8.18.3 .deb Package
    cd /tmp
    wget https://artifacts.elastic.co/downloads/beats/filebeat/filebeat-8.18.3-amd64.deb

ðŸ”¹ 2. Install the Package
    sudo dpkg -i filebeat-8.18.3-amd64.deb
    sudo apt-get install -f

ðŸ”¹ 3. Enable Filebeat to Start on Boot
    sudo systemctl enable filebeat
    systemctl start filebeat
    systemctl status filebeat
    journalctl -u filebeat -f

now config filebeat.yml as per your requirement.


root@ksa-processing-pr:/tmp# filebeat version
# Output: filebeat version 8.18.3 (amd64) ...
filebeat version 8.18.3 (amd64), libbeat 8.18.3 [ff779cdef575eea9e0b596a46e7182737805c2eb built 2025-06-18 17:02:15 +0000 UTC]




